title: Antwon performs "In Dark Denim" feat. Kerry McCoy of Deafheaven - Converse Rubber Tracks: Ready, Set
description:
Rapper Antwon is a soon-to-be Bay Area institution, riding a wave of blog buzz and guest verses to become one of San Francisco's most talked about artists. Partnering with guitarist Kerry McCoy of the superb Deafheaven, Antwon performed "In Dark Denim," a moody and visceral cut from the album of the same name out now on Greedhead. 

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
